{"tid":2421371,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企隻老貓貓(15-18歲)隻眼有事 唔知係白內障定青光眼","createTime":"2021-02-24T12:46:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T03:06:42.000Z","uid":114233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3989c17d5a0f0a27cba3e7c85cdd3a27ae109997","tid":2421371,"uid":114233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T12:46:36.000Z","msg":"我人住大埔，屋企有隻好老嘅貓近幾個月睇野唔係好清楚，好似睇野分唔到遠定近咁，行路成日差D撞到牆或者其他傢俬。 同埋隻左眼顏色變到有啲濛左咁，唔知係白內障定青光眼。有冇人知邊度睇醫生比較好。"},{"pid":"8c94c9e7664ea94fb8e9fb0df0bc297325873677","tid":2421371,"uid":114233,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:06:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TU0YOPf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTU0YOPf.jpg&h=630115fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對眼其實係黑色 反光問題右眼影左做紅色 但係左眼真係唔同左色 好耐冇帶過佢睇醫生 所以唔知宜家咩醫生比較好 有冇巴打絲打知我附近有啲咩收費正常又好嘅獸醫"},{"pid":"24ec317e6c6bf9d380c51f6243d8f991505d2bb6","tid":2421371,"uid":294380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:10:03.000Z","msg":"幫推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b94a08f0ff60944e6e7feabdcf401ef16c920d8","tid":2421371,"uid":308123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:10:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"332b3c261f9907c8de3be56647747fa02167702f","tid":2421371,"uid":301551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T14:45:19.000Z","msg":"你貓貓之前睇開邊個醫生呀？<br />\n我屋企果d睇開享和陳學維同梁振宇<br />\n睇左1x年"},{"pid":"16ee427edf920d51f918c37202ff7e5f36214590","tid":2421371,"uid":191673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T19:15:41.000Z","msg":"大埔可以睇普益歐醫生 大埔區內都算係咁，不過約左都要等好好好耐同reception啲人好無禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bf923d5436259ea49cb4b953ce00a49d5435463","tid":2421371,"uid":114233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16ee427edf920d51f9